{"tid":726092,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"2辣車時速200公里屯公狂飆　拐杖男司機被捕","createTime":"2018-07-02T06:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T05:46:00.000Z","uid":123587,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2f6e5e91790a48e278e9d0bb327bb7e303b1dd83","tid":726092,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"新界北總區交通部執行及管制組特遣隊人員，今晨(2日)近10時駕駛隱形戰車，沿屯門公路往荃灣方向巡邏，至近屯門富泰邨時，突有2輛福士辣車從後高速越過隱形戰車，警員隨即加速尾隨，期間以偵速器探測2車車速，發現其中一輛GTI辣車時速已超過200公里，警員於是響號追捕。<br />\n<br />\n隱形戰車於近深井將2車截停，2名司機落車助查，其中1人攜有拐杖，懷疑行動不便，其座駕的車頭擋風玻璃貼有傷殘人士標誌，該車的軚盤位置亦疑經過改裝，加裝了疑似手動控制油門的鐵杆，警方當場以涉嫌危險駕駛拘捕2車司機，涉案辣車拖走扣驗。"},{"pid":"e33df47b904a85aa0f8aa3698100bd303e6a0a77","tid":726092,"uid":35930,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:20:42.000Z","msg":"跛0既都揸咁快，厲害厲害"},{"pid":"6f4560d260e86d44e774cbdc791ad4ab3c70dce7","tid":726092,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:21:16.000Z","msg":"原來三隻腳真係揸得快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8996dca0b609061fe0027bb07d61835316f3b82","tid":726092,"uid":92278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:23:17.000Z","msg":"跛既都快過你"},{"pid":"0f44e560fdf0503e77a0b4eacb29f808cb0f1c33","tid":726092,"uid":44897,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/j8bdkaGhqtlhwGjd_rNJEJMYudY9F_PIA14D-zCPTu0wz3aGr5S4xo84F0czHsYaEmxnc9WbcyG833kVGqRG17hU0Vu-2M1JDauet2IYsXzWx6RZOHggOXL3ZvhleiGU9D1ZdtoBqiVpS38wBx9T3VUCkWHnMdo05KVjBv-AULJ2=w304-h484-nc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2Fj8bdkaGhqtlhwGjd_rNJEJMYudY9F_PIA14D-zCPTu0wz3aGr5S4xo84F0czHsYaEmxnc9WbcyG833kVGqRG17hU0Vu-2M1JDauet2IYsXzWx6RZOHggOXL3ZvhleiGU9D1ZdtoBqiVpS38wBx9T3VUCkWHnMdo05KVjBv-AULJ2%3Dw304-h484-nc&h=94d26ada&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cc04ec3cea99bbf9f2dfde3d492de5ca2407a7